  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he remembered me, and came up, and said, oh, my God, you're the man who didn't sell us passports, gave us passports, quite a few.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then it's all right, but then the Americans were responsible for getting them out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to already have their ticket, and they had to have a visa somewhere, Congo or anywhere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in most cases, for America, you see.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will say this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "America-- of course, America profited a lot from it by these brilliant people, but in the long run--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When it came down to it, they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't very helpful to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, they were trying to get us out as fast as they could because, you know, they were-- we were rocking the boat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Vichy was the government at that time, and they to-- they wanted to play ball with Vichy.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
